1. "Narednik* je naredio da se odmah uklone svi prepreke." (The sergeant ordered to immediately remove all obstacles.)

2. "Naredniku* su se pridružili još četiri pripadnika vojske." (Four more soldiers joined the sergeant.)

3. "On je narednikom* pokazao gdje je pronašao oružje." (He showed the sergeant where he found the weapon.)

4. "Ona je postala narednikom* posle samo jedne godine." (She became a sergeant after only one year.)

5. "Naredniku* su dali zadaću da istraži taj slučaj." (They gave the sergeant the task to investigate the case.)